https://leetcode.com/problems/sleep/submissions/1981040389

Code-

var sleep = function(millis) {
    return new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, millis));
};

------------------------------

Visual Flow-

sleep(100)
   ↓
setTimeout start
   ↓ (100ms wait)
resolve()
   ↓
.then() run

-------------------------------

Key Points-
-setTimeout create delay
-Promise make delay sync
-JS do not block (non-blocking)
-Exact time may differ

